23
00:02:00,896 --> 00:02:02,208
Don't let him escape! After him!

24
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:03,680
Lord Gao.

25
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:05,280
Who's there?

26
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:15,160
Boss! Boss! Boss!

27
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,560
(Shen Que...)

28
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,360
Ye Qinglan, the Lu family's concubine!

29
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,000
You defied feminine virtue

30
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,960
and seduced Governor-General Shen Que.

31
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:39,960
You entangled him during his return
to the capital,

32
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,400
and eloped with him,

33
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,640
causing his demise

34
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:45,560
and bringing imperial wrath
upon Ningzhou's people.

35
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:47,120
The Governor-General's death

36
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:50,160
was premeditated murder.

37
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:54,920
Lu Shi'an and I signed
a severance agreement long ago.

38
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,800
How dare you!

39
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,920
Shamelessly unrepentant.

40
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,040
How heinous!

41
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,800
Will you confess now?

42
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,720
Fabricated charges

43
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,520
need no justification.

44
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,720
I will not confess.

45
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,080
Fine! Harder!

46
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,000
Is this all you've got?

47
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,960
You can't win, Lord Xia.

48
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,760
Ye Qinglan,

49
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:36,480
Shen Que is dead.

50
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,920
Lu Shi'an is dead too.

51
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,920
In the end, I've won.

52
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,600
When I say you'll lose,

53
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,920
you'll lose.

54
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:53,560
Quit stalling.

55
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,840
Kill me.

56
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,080
Killing you?

57
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,400
Keep dreaming.

58
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,800
When the imperial censure comes,

59
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:08,320
you'll make a perfect scapegoat.

60
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,360
Tell me.

61
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:11,440
How would I kill you?

62
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:15,440
Guards!

63
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,080
Force her confession.

64
00:04:22,450 --> 00:04:24,224
