65
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,000
Imprison her securely.

66
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:28,840
Keep her alive.

67
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,120
This brazen criminal

68
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,640
