85
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,520
and murdered him.

86
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,760
How vicious this woman was!

87
00:05:13,856 --> 00:05:16,032
Defying womanly virtue,
you shamed all Ningzhou women!

88
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:16,400
- Pah!
- Pah!

89
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:16,880
- Pah!
- Pah!

90
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,200
- Pah!
- Pah!

91
