will appease the people,

95
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:33,400
and only a public execution
can uphold the law.

96
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:38,320
People of Ningzhou,
how shall I punish her?

97
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:41,280
- Burn her!
- Burn her!

98
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:43,280
I heard that Governor-General
was no good either.

99
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:45,160
The Prefect is virtuous and upright.

100
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:45,960
When bribes failed,

101
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,600
he tried framing the Prefect.

102
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,480
Without the Prefect,

103
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:51,400
Ningzhou would've burned
to ashes by pirates.

104
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,960
The Prefect is our sovereign.

105
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,000
This adulterous couple
deserves their deaths.

106
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:57,720
- Adulterous fools!
- They deserve death!

107
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,600
- They deserve death!
- They deserve death!

108
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,120
He's no corrupt official.

109
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,280
He was trying to help you.

110
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:06,680
- They deserve death!
- They deserve death!

111
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,720
Utter nonsense!

112
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,640
Let me heed the people's will.

113
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,480
Burn her!

114
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,240
Report!

115
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,120
My lord,

116
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:17,040
