has arrived.

117
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:17,680
What?

118
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,240
Why so sudden?

119
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,440
We didn't know
an official boat would come.

120
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:24,040
We thought it was just passing through.
It suddenly docked.

121
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,480
Never expected it to be Young Lord.

122
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,680
Come with me to greet him.

123
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,960
Hurry and wrap this up.

124
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,600
We mustn't let the Young Lord see this.

125
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:31,800
Yes.

126
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:32,760
Burn her!

127
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:33,800
Let's go.

128
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:40,960
Let me send you on your final journey.

129
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,440
Who dares block the Young Lord's path?

130
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,520
Do you want to die?

131
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:15,720
My lord, you misunderstood.
This woman eloped with her lover.

132
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:18,040
She also conspired
with bandits for wealth

133
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,160
and murdered her man.

134
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:22,080
Only execution will satisfy
the people's outrage.

135
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,760
My lord, I venture

136
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:34,200
