137
00:07:54,432 --> 00:07:56,080
You risked death to stop my procession.

138
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,360
For whom do you seek justice?

139
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:02,240
I seek justice for my deceased husband.

140
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,560
Raise your head.

141
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,840
Who

142
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,920
