158
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:28,840
The name Shen Que
was bestowed by His Majesty,

159
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,840
so that I might serve him.

160
00:09:30,976 --> 00:09:32,720
Took the surname
from the Empress Dowager.

161
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,080
I am Yin Ruxing, Duke of Xuan,

162
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:40,320
the very one you named.

